    <briefdescription>
<para>Function pointer to register the routes. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>WebSocket endpoint that queues messages and dispatches JSON commands.</para>
<para>Incoming multi-frame messages are captured as <ref refid="class_c_web_socket_message" kindref="compound">CWebSocketMessage</ref> objects, queued, and later dispatched from the application loop. Selected commands can require authentication before they are processed. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
